refsect1.para:

     Exemple avec krsort


<?php
  $fruits = array("d"=>"papaye","a"=>"orange","b"=>"banane","c"=>"ananas");
  ksort($fruits);
  for(reset($fruits); $key = key($fruits); next($fruits)) {
    echo "fruits[$key] = ".$fruits[$key]."\n";
  }
?>



    Cet exemple va afficher :


fruits[a] = orange
fruits[b] = banane
fruits[c] = ananas
fruits[d] = papaye
